FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773144742
OL,3,CWet February dampens retail sales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict threat to
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FJack Meaning, chief UK economist at
OL,8,FBarclays, said: "This timely insight
OL,9,Finto consumers' reaction to the
OL,10,Fevolving situation in the Middle East
OL,11,Fhighlights perfectly the economic
OL,12,Frisks for the UK if the conflict
OL,13,Fdoesn't find a way to de-escalate in
OL,14,Fshort order.
OL,16,F"The start of 2026 had brought
OL,17,Fpositive signs of growth and improving
OL,18,Fconsumer sentiment. A new, prolonged
OL,19,Fbout of uncertainty risks snuffing
OL,20,Fthat out before it has had a chance to
OL,21,Freally get going."
OL,26,@pD@QOUxD@AOU}D@RO]
